description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for an enthusiastic and committed Administrator to join our Physical Health team within the Nursing and Quality directorate based on the Blackberry Hill site in Bristol.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are keen to appoint a team administrator to help support the Head of Physical Health and wider multi-disciplinary team that incorporates health promotion, practice development, resuscitation and medical devices.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an interesting and varied role. Good team working is essential as you will be the key to maintaining consistent and efficient service delivery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a part time post working 30 hours a week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Lynn Jacob on 0117 3784459, email lynnjacob@nhs.net for further information&lt;/p&gt;
